channel.title: Other Person Loggin In Freezing Me Help
channel.description: Hey, im having this problem when my friend logs in while im in or i try to log in while he is in, My game freezes. It didnt do this when he started with me but since he got a bit higher (stats, Game time ect) It freezes. Any ideas how to fix? (This is my Moparscape Client that freezes not my server)
